Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.27,0:01:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't break it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.77,0:01:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The skull mark is a symbol of faith!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.15,0:01:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a direct hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:02:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zoan-Type Devil Fruit!\NChopper's Seven-Form Transformation"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.36,0:02:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've been blown away!\NSuch an idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.11,0:02:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? It didn't break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.79,0:02:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Can't be... He's stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.49,0:02:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know who the heck\Nthis pirate flag belongs to...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but since this flag is a person's\Npledge to risk his life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's not raised as a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This flag isn't something you can\Njust break while laughing foolishly!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:58.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.08,0:03:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is... a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.05,0:03:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a symbol of the belief\Nthat nothing is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will save this country as a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.06,0:03:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By raising this,\NI'll fight just like pirates do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are incredible guys at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.50,0:03:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cool to be a pirate!\NThere're tons of incredible guys at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.47,0:03:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper, go out to sea some day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.75,0:03:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hmm?\N--Hey, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna beat these guys up now.\NWhat do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying? You damn idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:45.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna protect the flag that bad,\Nstay there forever to protect it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop... right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.50,0:03:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.27,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your backbone gave out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.81,0:04:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just natural.\NYou're moving around too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.11,0:04:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, doctor's orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.32,0:04:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you idiots doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just stand there and watch!\NI'll blow him to bits along with that flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to get blown away, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.94,0:04:31.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the idea! Get him, reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.41,0:04:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol-sama! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.78,0:04:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The little brat is showing his guts\Nas if he's a fully grown man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.06,0:04:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I won't let you lay\Nyour finger on Wapol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, there are some strange\Ncreatures in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.97,0:05:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like you're that "yeti" the citizens\Ngot worked up about at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must really have spent your\Nwhole life disliked by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor monster. Why's a loner like\Nyou trying to save this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Even if I don't have friends,\NI can still fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Doctor's flag exists, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do have friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.46,0:05:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just fine...\Nsince I'm a rubber man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.60,0:06:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A rubber man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, reindeer. Can you finish that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like that is a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.61,0:06:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My opponent is the annoying mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.88,0:06:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Straw Hat,\Nflying around like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't hesitate any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can take me down?!\NHuh, you monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.49,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Old hag! I will fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.10,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.47,0:06:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep moving around, you won't\Nbe able to walk on your own anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.57,0:06:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. When push comes to shove,\Nmy reindeer can handle things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Tony Tony Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:54.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a name that the world's\Ngreatest doctor gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if Doctor forgave you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you for\Nlaughing at how he lived!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.27,0:07:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who'll show\Nno forgiveness! I'll stomp you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:18.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! Dalton-san! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please! Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.12,0:07:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Dalton-san! Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.95,0:07:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.76,0:07:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Twenty MDs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His body is frozen. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.93,0:07:43.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you leave him in our care?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there are doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I heard that there weren't\Nany doctors in this country...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These guys're called the Twenty MDs\Nand they exclusively work for Wapol.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.15,0:07:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, they're bad doctors!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! We can't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.12,0:08:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave Dalton-san in your care when\Nyou gave in to Wapol... to the king?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you going to do to Dalton-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to save him,\Njust do what we say!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are still doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we were forced to give\Nin by Wapol and his men's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.14,0:08:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we've always worked to advance\Nour medical research...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.34,0:08:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the patients in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.18,0:08:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was because a certain quack\Ntaught us not to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose any more...\Nstupid men like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.96,0:08:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The effect of the Rumble Ball\Nlasts 3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.83,0:08:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you down in 3 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 minutes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't defeat me at all,\Nmuch less in 3 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 minutes? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 minutes? That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.11,0:09:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to see something interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! Let me fight, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.15,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumble!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What... did you say you could do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.13,0:09:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marimo's Snow Melting Arrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.33,0:09:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk Point! Leg boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.47,0:09:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! Just a transformation?!\NI was expecting something more!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you have\Nthe powers of a devil fruit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoan-type, just like Dalton!\NA reindeer human, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.98,0:09:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy Point! Weight Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.49,0:09:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.59,0:09:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything about the three-form\Ntransformation you Zoan-types use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.56,0:09:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marimo's Super Surprise Quattro Hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen all your forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.77,0:09:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're a\Npower fighter like Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.94,0:10:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's no way you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.41,0:10:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jumping Point! Jump Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...outpower me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.72,0:10:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He jumped! He can really jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's that form?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.66,0:10:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't his "human-animal form" the little\Nreindeer from earlier?! How impudent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guard Point! Fur Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.71,0:10:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.99,0:10:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be... I hit him dead on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.66,0:10:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.56,0:10:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was sure that Zoan-types\Nhad a limit of three forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.33,0:10:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.00,0:11:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Rumble Ball is a drug
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.90,0:11:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that messes up the wavelength\Nof the devil fruit's transformations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.07,0:11:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,During my 5 years of research,\NI found 4 more transformation points.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.41,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 transformations plus 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seven-form transformation?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sev...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.85,0:11:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big deal with the\Nnumber of transformations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.18,0:11:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A seven-form transforming\Ninteresting reindeer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.49,0:11:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.42,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like his happiness exceeded its limit\Nafter hearing seven-phase transformation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... What happened\Nto your fight against me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To hell with seven-phase transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.48,0:11:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be deceived by such a sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.02,0:12:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a sham!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arm Point! Arm Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:30.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me tell you one thing.\NMy iron hooves can smash even rocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.73,0:12:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How impudent, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.50,0:12:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll show you! Marimo's Surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quattro Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.80,0:12:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow Splitting Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.54,0:12:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... The castle wall got hollowed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.28,0:13:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! He dodged it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, how about... this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.92,0:13:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Omnidirectional Snow Splitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.50,0:13:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your\Nhigh spirits from earlier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.44,0:13:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't win if you just\Nkeep dodging, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.92,0:13:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brain Point! Brain Boost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I was just dodging.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking for your weak spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will finish you. Scope!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A... A beam!\NHe'll definitely shoot a beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.78,0:14:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's definitely a beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone says,\Nit's a beam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.08,0:14:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What else could it be?! It's a beam!\N--How can you know?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I just know! It's a beam! Beam!\N--How can you know?! Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.42,0:14:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I just know! It's a beam! Beam!\N--Then what kind of beam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should use this chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.42,0:14:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for\Nmy weak spot?! So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a blind spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a transforming idiot\Nwho can't even attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.97,0:14:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who'll be finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.68,0:14:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.28,0:14:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His jaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:15:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoofprint...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.84,0:15:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Roseo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.13,0:15:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, reindeer!\NYou're pretty good, reindeer! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Dalton-san!\N--Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, let's go up the mountain,\NUsopp-san, Mr. Bushido!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.29,0:15:57.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just sit around and wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.63,0:16:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried what happened to Luffy-san\Nand the others in that big avalanche!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.77,0:16:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san has a very high fever!\NIf anything happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.54,0:16:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're worried about Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of that, you're worried about\NDalton-san as well as Alabasta, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivi, calm down! You're carrying\Ntoo many burdens on your shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami is with Luffy and Sanji.\NI'm sure she's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.86,0:16:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be fine! I believe in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right... He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san believes in his friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he can be so calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Usopp-san. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, it's just that you're afraid\Nof going up the mountain, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.65,0:16:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B... But I heard that there're things\Nlike a yeti and bear-bunnies there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then say so from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.19,0:16:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine. It's Luffy we're\Ntalking about. He'll make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help it if I'm scared!\NAny problem with that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.93,0:17:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.76,0:17:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.40,0:17:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.57,0:17:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would someone please tell me\Nwho the heck this guy is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my way! We can't\Nlet Wapol in the castle! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.25,0:17:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're\Nheading to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your condition... that's reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.62,0:17:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will I fight if I don't fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Wapol goes back to being the king,\Nthis country will become rotten forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way you can fight\Nin that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.46,0:17:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're no match for them, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle this! No matter\Nhow dirty I have to play!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on my back.\NI'll take you to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be modest!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna waste your\Ndetermination. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.63,0:18:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.83,0:18:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, okay? I will take you...\Nto the castle now...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.72,0:18:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Usopp-kun. I really don't\Nthink this is going to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll work! I'll take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna fight for the country, right?!\NYou're gonna settle this, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. I'll definitely take you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... that moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.57,0:18:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to go up the mountain, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.54,0:19:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You jerk! You jerk! Usopp Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.35,0:19:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ow! Ow! What're you doing?!\N--You jerk! You jerk! Usopp Punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to use my serious power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.79,0:19:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.46,0:19:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Serious Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.19,0:19:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Whoa, amazing, amazing...\N--Serious Power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! If you're willing to\Ngo that far to get there...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.23,0:19:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a ropeway to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.14,0:19:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't be. There's no rope\Nconnected to the castle any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one. Someone has\Nreattached a white rope...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...from a big tree at the\Nedge of Gyasta to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gyasta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name of the town\Nthat Dr. Kureha headed last.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.99,0:19:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That tin bastard! He's disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Ahhh! Ahhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He came up on the haired hippo.\NHe wouldn't go down on his own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.74,0:20:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When on earth did he...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.74,0:20:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While you were fascinated by\Nthe transformations, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.98,0:20:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! I'll find him\Nright away and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.52,0:20:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he got into\Nthe castle from somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.75,0:20:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, Nami-san will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.42,0:20:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! If he lays\Nhis hands on Nami-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hold it!\N--I'll gut him 100 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, does he want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.57,0:20:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He called me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.44,0:20:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you, annoying mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.59,0:20:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like my fever is\Ncoming down quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.66,0:21:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it's likely that\NI can go back to the ship soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.80,0:21:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time to be in bed resting here!\NVivi is waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.05,0:21:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.88,0:21:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really my Drum Castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.35,0:21:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have they done to my castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.96,0:21:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will chew up every single one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.41,0:21:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.72,0:22:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.83,0:22:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.11,0:22:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.59,0:22:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:22:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should get out of here quickly\Nwhile Doctorine isn't around!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.02,0:23:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard! I'll find him\Nright away and finish him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.92,0:23:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he lays his hands on Nami-san,\NI'll gut him 100 times!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.69,0:23:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! He looks like a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.59,0:23:08.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've cornered you, annoying mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san's got dynamites!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.93,0:23:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what's going on here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.23,0:23:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.60,0:23:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When The Kingdom's Rule Ends!\NThe Flag of Faith Flies Forever"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.40,0:23:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
